<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="honesty-n">honesty <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɒnəsti/    美 /'ɑːnəsti/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>诚实；正直：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Honesty, my mum always used to tell me, is the best policy.
我妈妈过去总是跟我说，诚实是最好的策略。</p><footer>2011 湖北</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-all-honesty">in all honesty</h3>
<p>1.<strong>说实话；其实：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In all honesty, my university is not as well-known as my "dream" university.
说实话，我上的那所大学不如我理想中的大学出名。</p></div></div>